'''Solitaire''' was a game meant for one [[Sentience/Legends|person]] to play. The term also referred to a situation in which one side was acting as another to give the impression that there was no second side.

==Behind the scenes==
Solitaire was mentioned in [[2002]] novel ''[[The New Jedi Order: Dark Journey]]'', written by [[Elaine Cunningham]]. It is a real-world game.

